  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this prospective randomized controlled trial was to compare intensive insulin
      therapy with a carbohydrate restrictive strategy in patients with acute ischemic stroke
      evaluating the outcome through the Glasgow Outcome Scale Extended, hospital mortality and
      NIHSS during the ICU stay.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
